                  </hi> I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">read—Abraham Robinson, convicted</hi> 1<hi rend="italic">st Jan.</hi>, 1846, <hi rend="italic">and confined six months</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
